  "text": "In Fig. 5 , the polarity effects were plotted with the depth very similar to the data presented in TG-106. [CITATION_1] The differences among these chambers were within 1% at shallow region ≤ 19 cm, except buildup region. Although the Sun Nuclear and IBA scanning systems used the same type of ionization chambers, differences ≥ 1% were observed at deeper depths.",
